<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Verify your email â€“ Lineup</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background-color: #1a1a2e; padding: 32px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
    .body { padding: 32px; color: #333333; }
    .body p { line-height: 1.6; }
    .code-wrapper { margin: 28px 0; text-align: center; }
    .code { display: inline-block; letter-spacing: 10px; font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a2e; background-color: #f4f4f4; border: 2px dashed #e94560; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px 32px; }
    .expiry { margin-top: 8px; font-size: 13px; color: #999999; }
    .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee; margin: 24px 0; }
    .warning { font-size: 13px; color: #999999; line-height: 1.5; }
    .footer { background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 16px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #999999; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Verify your email</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Hi <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>Thanks for signing up to Lineup! Use the verification code below to confirm your email address and activate your account.</p>
      <div class="code-wrapper">
        <span class="code">{{code}}</span>
        <p class="expiry">This code expires in <strong>{{expiresIn}}</strong>.</p>
      </div>
      <hr class="divider" />
      <p class="warning">If you did not create an account with Lineup, you can safely ignore this email. Someone may have entered your address by mistake.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} Lineup. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
